(\(each a "Party" and collectively the "Parties"\)) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(1. PURPOSE) Tj T*
(The Parties intend to explore a potential business collaboration and may disclose) Tj T*
(confidential information to each other for evaluation purposes.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(2. DEFINITION OF CONFIDENTIAL INFORMATION) Tj T*
("Confidential Information" means any non-public information disclosed by one Party) Tj T*
(to the other, including but not limited to: business plans, technical data, source code,) Tj T*
(customer lists, financial information, and trade secrets.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(3. OBLIGATIONS) Tj T*
(Each Party agrees to: \(a\) hold all Confidential Information in strict confidence;) Tj T*
(\(b\) not disclose Confidential Information to any third party without prior written) Tj T*
(consent; \(c\) use Confidential Information solely for the purpose stated herein.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(4. TERM) Tj T*
(This Agreement is effective as of March 15, 2026, and shall remain in force for) Tj T*
(a period of two \(2\) years, expiring on March 14, 2028.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(5. NOTICE PERIOD) Tj T*
(Either party may terminate with sixty \(60\) days written notice. Confidentiality) Tj T*
(obligations survive termination for the full two-year term.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(6. EXCEPTIONS) Tj T*
(Obligations do not apply to information that: \(a\) is or becomes publicly known) Tj T*
(through no breach of this Agreement; \(b\) was already known to the receiving Party;) Tj T*
(\(c\) is required to be disclosed by law or court order.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(7. NO LICENSE) Tj T*
(Nothing herein grants any license or right to use the other Party's intellectual) Tj T*
(property except as explicitly stated.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(8. AUTO-RENEWAL) Tj T*
(This Agreement automatically renews for successive one-year periods unless either) Tj T*
(Party provides written notice of non-renewal at least sixty \(60\) days before the) Tj T*
(end of the then-current term.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(9. GOVERNING LAW) Tj T*
(This Agreement is governed by Swedish law. Disputes shall be resolved exclusively) Tj T*
(in Stockholm District Court.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
